OL,3,C'Progress is being made' in tackling
OL,4,Cracism in football, Premier League CEO
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe head of the Premier League said
OL,8,Fwork still needs to be done to tackle
OL,9,Fracism in football, but he pointed to
OL,10,Fseveral recent successes in clamping
OL,11,Fdown on its online presence, ITV News
OL,12,FSports Editor Steve Scott reports.
OL,14,FThe head of the Premier League has
OL,15,Fsaid there has been "progress" in the
OL,16,Feffort to stamp out racism in football
OL,17,Fafter Jess Carter was subject to abuse
OL,18,Fduring the 2025 Euros.
