OL,3,C'Progress is being made' in tackling
OL,4,Cracism in football, Premier League CEO
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FCarter suffered a torrid time during
OL,8,Fthe tournament after being targeted by
OL,9,Fracial abuse online, which forced her
OL,10,Foff social media.
OL,12,FShe was dropped for the semi-final
OL,13,Fwhen the Lionesses decided not to
OL,14,F'take the knee' in protest of her
OL,15,Ftreatment online, but she was
OL,16,Freinstated for the final against Spain.
OL,18,FSpeaking to ITV News, Carter said she
OL,19,Fwas scared to play the final, which
OL,20,Fshe said was a first for her.
