OL,3,C'Progress is being made' in tackling
OL,4,Cracism in football, Premier League CEO
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"I think it was a mixture of such a
OL,8,Fbig game, but then on top of that, (I
OL,9,Fwas) scared of whatever abuse might
OL,10,Fcome with it, whether it's football-
OL,11,Fbased or whether it was going to be
OL,12,Fthe racial abuse that was going to
OL,13,Fcome with it because I did something
OL,14,Fwrong," she said.
OL,16,FCarter said the abuse she received
OL,17,F"makes you feel really small".
