OL,3,C'Progress is being made' in tackling
OL,4,Cracism in football, Premier League CEO
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"It makes you feel like you're not
OL,8,Fimportant, that you're not valuable,"
OL,9,Fshe added. "It makes you second-guess
OL,10,Feverything that you do - it's not a
OL,11,Fnice place to be. It doesn't make me
OL,12,Ffeel confident going back onto the
OL,13,Fpitch."
OL,15,FShe said she feared teammate Lauren
OL,16,FJames would suffer "astronomical"
OL,17,Fracist abuse if she had been the only
OL,18,FEngland played to miss a penalty in
OL,19,Fthe quarter final against Sweden.
