OL,4,Cracism in football, Premier League CEO
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FCarter said she felt "relief" when
OL,8,Fsome of her white teammates also
OL,9,Fmissed.
OL,11,F"It's horrible to say but it's almost
OL,12,Flike a sigh of relief when other
OL,13,Fplayers that weren't black missed a
OL,14,Fpenalty, because the racism that would
OL,15,Fhave come with LJ (Lauren James) being
OL,16,Fthe only one that missed would have
OL,17,Fbeen astronomical," she added.
