OL,4,Cracism in football, Premier League CEO
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FShe said: "From the start of the
OL,8,Ftournament I have experienced a lot of
OL,9,Fracial abuse.
OL,11,F"Whilst I feel every fan is entitled
OL,12,Fto their opinion on performance and
OL,13,Fresult I don't agree or think it's ok
OL,14,Fto target someone's appearance or
OL,15,Frace."
OL,17,FFormer Leicester City player Wes
OL,18,FMorgan told ITV News that they believe
OL,19,Fthe social media giants are not doing
OL,20,Fenough to stop it on their platform.
